task.summary: + Travelling screen GUI + All crewmembers dying now leads to game over + Ship can now sink if ship health = 0 leading to a game over + Events scurvy, English marine raid, Pirate attack + Game can now be won by reaching the final town + Bug fixed where you would randomly be teleported to the next town while your distance travelled would stay the same, leading to extremely long travelling + Crew now only consumes as much food as members are alive
+ Player is now given a final score when they complete or lose the game which saves to a .txt file
